data.title: Meghan Markle turns 43 today and here's 11 incredible photos of her
data.meta_description: Meghan Markle is celebrating her 43rd birthday today, August 4 and Express.co.uk takes a look at some of her best moments over the years.
data.text:
Meghan Markle is celebrating her 43rd birthday today, with the former working royal likely marking the day with Prince Harry and their two children in California.

Born on August 4, 1981, Meghan was the youngest of three - having two elder half-siblings, Thomas Markle Jr and Samantha Markle.

She is the only child of Doria Ragland, while Thomas Markle Sr is father to her half-siblings.

Her parents split up when she was just six years old and, although now estranged from her father, Meghan has remained close to her mother.
